posts.name: Guilherme Samuel
posts.cooked: I watched an episode called Rewind about the history of control systems and decided to clone a 2006 robot code repository into my machine. Finding it fascinating, I began comparing older and newer control systems and programming techniques. Following this interest, I wanted to explore more resources on the history of control systems over the years. Recalling some useful materials from previous projects, I stumbled upon Team358’s resources page, which features a timeline spanning various years.
